column16: Dewayne Wise grounds out, first baseman Anthony Rizzo to pitcher Alex Burnett.
Tyler Flowers pops out to third baseman Luis Valbuena.
Jeff Keppinger singles on a ground ball to center fielder David DeJesus.
Conor Gillaspie flies out to left fielder Scott Hairston.
Evan Longoria hits a ground-rule double (11) on a fly ball down the right-field line.

Desmond Jennings singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Adam Jones.   Jose Lobaton scores.    Yunel Escobar scores.  Desmond Jennings advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by center fielder Adam Jones.
Yunel Escobar hits a ground-rule double (7) on a line drive to center field.   Luke Scott scores.    Jose Lobaton to 3rd.
Mike Moustakas lines out to left fielder Nate McLouth.
Salvador Perez singles on a pop up to first baseman Chris Davis.   Alex Gordon scores.
Billy Butler grounds out, shortstop J.   Hardy to first baseman Chris Davis.   Alex Gordon to 2nd.
